title: Babes Are Wolves - 2014 - Demo
description:
Babes Are Wolves hail from Adelaide, SA. Their love for Sean Connery and dirty jokes inspires these girls to make the moody catchy tunes they do, blending rock, grunge and dark pop into tunes that would romance your mum. An energetic live act, they have already supported bands such as Axe Girl (WA), Hey, Lady! (NSW), Captives (Melb) and Tony Font Show (SA).

These are their demo tracks released in 2014.

 
http://www.babesarewolves.net/
